column2: SELECT m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, s.* into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.MyTable AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN apogeestar s ON s.apstar_id = o.objidSELECT m.sourceid, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, s.* FROM MyDB.MyTable AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN apogeestar s ON s.apstar_id = o.objid
